      "title": "Sri Lanka schedules power cuts of 2 hours 20 mins from Aug 30 \u2013 Sept 02",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Power cuts of 2 hours and 20 minutes would be imposed on around Sri Lanka from August 30 to September 02, 2022 Public Utilities Commission Chairman Janaka Ratnayake said.",
        "Groups ABCDEFGHIJKLPQRSTUVW will have one hour cuts during the daytime and 1 hour and 20 minutes of power cut during the night.",
        "Sri Lanka\u2019s had power cuts increased to 3 hours from 0 hour in August after 300 MegaWatt coal plant went down.",
        "Related Sri Lanka may reduce power cuts after coal plant repair",
        "The CEB has said due to lack of fuel power, cuts cannot be reduced to one hour. (Colombo/Aug30/2022)"
      ],
